property.description:
Specify the e-mail address of the sender ( 
                                    MAIL FROM
                                    ). If not specified, the configuration uses the e-mail address of the recipient.

object.description:
The host name/IP address pairs that are currently stored in the DNS cache. A new entry is stored each time DataPower successfully looks up a host name on a DNS server. The name can be either fully qualified (for example, 
            servername.uk.ibm.com
            ), or a partial host name (for example, 
            servername
            ).

